Detailed Description

template<typename ETYPE>
class OOArray< ETYPE >

NSMutableArray wrapper allowing subscript syntax by index and various other operators. The integer value of an OArray object is the number of elements e.g. "for ( i=0 ; i<array ; i++ )".

operatorinplacebinaryargument
assignment =array
copy <<=array
add object(s)+=+object (or array)
remove object(s)-=-object (or array)
replicate members(s)*=*count
split alternate members/count e.g 2 for even/odd members
filter array&=&array
merge array|=|array
subscript []int, object or range

	OOArray array;
 }

     array += @"STRING"; // append to array
     array[1] = @"STRING"; // set position directly
     NSString *str = &array[1]; // take polinter to item 1
     ~array[0]; // remove element at position 0
 }
